## Fee Impact by Strategy

```
Category: Geopolitics (0% taker fee)
├─ Basket Arb Threshold: 0.5% edge
├─ Strategy Viability: ✅ BEST CATEGORY
└─ Example: $10,000 position × 0.5% = $50 profit minimum

Category: Sports (0.75% taker fee)
├─ Basket Arb Threshold: 2.0% edge
├─ Strategy Viability: ✅ GOOD
└─ Example: $10,000 position × 2.0% = $200 profit minimum

Category: Politics (1.00% taker fee)
├─ Basket Arb Threshold: 2.5% edge
├─ Strategy Viability: ✅ VIABLE
└─ Example: $10,000 position × 2.5% = $250 profit minimum

Category: Crypto (1.80% taker fee)
├─ Basket Arb Threshold: 4.1% edge
├─ Strategy Viability: ⚠️ DIFFICULT
└─ Example: $10,000 position × 4.1% = $410 profit minimum
└─ Note: Latency arb dead—MM/ACS only

Maker Rebates (Compensates Fees)
├─ Base: 20% of taker fees collected
├─ Finance: 50% of taker fees (BEST REBATE)
├─ Example: You earn rebates even if users trade against you
└─ This is the #1 structural edge in 2026
```

