## Risk Management Hierarchy

```
┌─ Portfolio Level
│  ├─ Daily loss limit: -2%
│  ├─ Total exposure: <100% of capital
│  ├─ Halt trading if limit hit
│  └─ Reset daily P&L tracking at EOD
│
├─ Position Level
│  ├─ Max per trade: 5%
│  ├─ Kelly sizing: quarter Kelly (not full)
│  ├─ Event cluster limit: 20%
│  └─ One-sided exposure: 30% max
│
├─ Order Level
│  ├─ Limit orders only (no market orders unless gross edge > threshold)
│  ├─ Cancel orders 2 min before events
│  ├─ Adverse selection detection
│  └─ Inventory rebalancing
│
└─ System Level
    ├─ Staleness detection (>5s = alert)
    ├─ Connection monitoring
    ├─ Rate limit enforcement
    └─ Emergency stop procedure
```

